==Tailoring==
The Morel is used in the spool of the [[2 Willow Lane#Sewing Machine|Sewing Machine]] to create the [[Tailoring|Morel Shirt]].  [[File:Shirt257.png|24px]] It can be used in [[dyeing]], serving as an orange dye at the dye pots, located in [[Emily]]'s and [[Haley]]'s house, [[2 Willow Lane]].

==Quests==
The Morel is not used in any [[quests]].

==History==
{{History|1.4|Can now be used in [[Tailoring]].}}

